  "textPreview": "Free June 9 event: How to win brand visibility when AI decides what gets seen →\nSolutions\nTools\nResources\nPricing\nEN\nSign in\nRequest a demo\nStart free trial\nKeyword Tool\n\nA data-driven keyword research tool that helps you assess keyword potential and uncover thousands of ideas to fuel your SEO and PPC campaigns.\n\nUnited States\nAnalyze\nUnique database that delivers keyword suggestions for any market\n3.2B\nEUROPE\n1.2B\nNORTH AMERICA\n542M\nASIA\nDo keyword research like a pro with essential data at your fingertips\nKeyword Overview\nSERP Overview\nRelated keywords\nLocal keywords\nMore keyword ideas\nSee the full story behind any keyword\n\nGet a complete overview of your target keyword with our Keyword Tool, including all essential metrics, and in your chosen location and timeframe. Start your keyword research smart with data you can rely on.\n\nTest drive our Keyword Generator to explore its full potential\n\nTry it free for 14 days to see how it can streamline your SEO workflow!\n\nStart free trial\nSee product tour\n\nNo credit card required\n\nGet key SEO metrics for data-driven keyword research\n1\nSearch volume\n\nFind out how many monthly organic searches the selected keyword gets on Google. Evaluate last year’s changes by reviewing the keyword’s volume dynamics.\n\nKeyword difficulty\nCPC\nSearch Intent\nLocal keyword data\n1\n2\n3\n4\n5\nStart free trial\nSupport your strategy with in-depth competitor keyword analysis\n\nDiscover what’s been working for your competitors and use those insights to refine your keyword strategy\n\nCompetitor Keyword Research\nOrganic SERP History\nAds History\nFind your competitors’ target keywords\n\nAnalyze the keywords driving traffic to your competitors' sites. View complete keyword lists with essential metrics, including search volume, difficulty, search intent, and current rankings. Identify gaps in your strategy, discover opportunities, and prioritize keywords that deliver results in your niche.\n\nScale keyword research with SE Ranking’s API\n\nQuickly analyze large volume",
